Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! You're forgetting something!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the menu today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's omelet rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks... now, don't you be late, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So in this place, every single student\Nhas some special ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:22.43,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2\NMelody of Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, some have the possibility of having one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,some show signs of developing one...\Nthere are many students of such pending nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But transferring just for that..?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, those who had \Nspecial abilities like us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbecame guinea pigs for neuroscientists without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you get caught even once, \Nyour life is basically over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hah... such a hyperbole...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually talking about my big brother..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To protect those with abilities,\Na certain individual created the current system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though it wasn't in time \Nto save my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you were the one that got me into\Nthis student council, and to use my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The student council is the only group\Nthat is entrusted with a special mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mission is to get a hold of those with abilities\Nout on the loose, like you were, before others...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and either protect them\Nor threaten them to never use their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In return, you are paid appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Ayumi doing her best to make
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,meals every day because you \Ncan't even afford proper food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm Yu Otosaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came here from Hinomori High School.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's a first year,\Nbut she's the student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. In this academy, the student council president\Nis not determined by grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The highest priority goes to someone with an ability,\Nand how active they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly the same \Nthing as last night's dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka, what are you \Ngoing to do about lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't have anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go to the cafeteria together.\NI'll guide you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to invite her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, I can invite her as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nah... no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be\Nany open seats at the tables...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we buy some sandwiches\Nand go back to the classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's pretty crowded over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that part to me.\NIt's where I can show off my own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for you to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'll go in from \Nthe blind spot on the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, since it will go by too quickly,\Nwhat kind of bread I grab all depends on luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, today I have a marvelous \Nresult. A cutlet sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You call that a success?\NWith so many wounds all over you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do wear armor under my uniform\Nso the wounds are not that deep, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you're bleeding from your head!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're... a pretty dangerous \Nguy, despite how you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More like, you have nothing \Nbut cutlet sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's teleportation, you know?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I had time to \Npick and choose what I wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And every single one is smushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's teleportation, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can fine-tune\Nhow forcefully I grab the merchandise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's an imperfect ability!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't even have any female friends,\Nthough she's the student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her ability is to become invisible\Nto one person she chooses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, everyone other than\Nthat one person can see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such imperfection is what caused \Nthe situation she is currently in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she had valid reason to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would people around her think after\Nseeing her use her ability
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take violent actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of it, the surveillance cameras show\Nnothing more than an ordinary fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she kept doing something like that,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's pretty obvious that people \Nwould come to hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But her personality apparently wasn't like that\Nuntil she got into middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's coming towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A comrade will show up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means, everyone gather\Nat the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You figured it out with just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world is going to begin..?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ability... is thoughtography..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A comrade that tells us the location and power\Nof someone who possesses a special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nanba High School... I guess we'll do a stakeout.\NLet's go, we're going to leave school early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To do some investigation, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're not the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the police you mention \Nfinds this person before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthat person's life is completely done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously..?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Start asking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should begin as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, ask whether or not something strange\Nhas been going on lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, since the ability\Nhas been determined as thoughtography,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it might be good to ask about\Nany rumors that involve photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I have time for this...\Nthey're nothing more than lunatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone acting suspiciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take over his body with your ability,\Nand look through his belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To protect the one who \Nhas the special ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,....Fine! Which guy is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, don't make me spend so much time!\NI lost sight of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found him! That's the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, why do I have to \Ndo something like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Photographs of a female student \Nattending this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next up... well... a girl in her lingerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is thoughtography?\NYou sure use it for something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take these pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I bought them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you buy them from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend of leaking any of this to a third party.\NPlease tell me just the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell us, I'll tell the girl in this photograph\Nthat this was in your possession..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Udoh... in class 2-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're out to capture Udoh from 2-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has Udoh gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Udoh is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I'm going to \Nexcuse myself before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if this isn't a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have though that the culprit\Nthat takes lewd photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,like this with his thoughtography ability,\Nand selling them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...was the captain of the archery team?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Photograph? Thoughtography?\NI don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One of your customers spilled the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and we did look through your locker, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A ton of photos came out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso I recorded them all on this video camera as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily open something\Nlike a locker inside a clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's because I \Ncan make money with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something involving \Nyour family's finances?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents wouldn't be happy\Nreceiving money made in such a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're sick! There's nothing else I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I projected you in your lingerie here.\NThe image includes your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want this photo \Ndistributed everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Npretend like none of this ever happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you have to do for a thoughtography?\NThat sure is something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, nobody would ever \Nneed something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who looks at you, \Nyou're an attractive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got a compliment! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so hurry up and get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The photo is... gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate. Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend like none of this ever happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst kind of person\Nto point an arrow at someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how much martial arts \Nspirit you possess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We really don't plan on tossing you over\Nto the police or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:13:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you keep using those powers,\Nyour life will be completely ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be an experimental sample\Nto be dissected by scientists or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dissected!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a warning. Those powers will be gone\Nonce your adolescence has passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for money, please earn some\Nby working legitimate part-time jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We took care of that successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you guys always do things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so that no one with special abilities\Nend up facing what my big brother has faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... so, what actually happened to your big brother\Nafter he got caught by the scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing worth hiding in the end.\NWould you like to visit tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To where my big brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to pass. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten lunch yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's buy station-specific \Nlunches at the kiosk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.43,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beef Tongue Lunch Box
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one! This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The beef tongue bento box lunch\Nthat warms up when you pull a string!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this just amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't think it would \Nbe an express train...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can she eat in a situation like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's totally ill-mannered to do so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're not going to eat your sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother was the first \Nto have a special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was back when I passed the \Nmiddle school entrance exams
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nfor a magnet school of a national university.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Mom, I did it! I got accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really did do your best, Nao!\NThat truly means you'll end up an expert doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, look at this! I got accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? You're so amazing, unlike me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you're more amazing \Nthan me, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the record companies\Nare taking note of your band!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're poor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry up and debut\Nfrom a major record label and live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you listen to \Nthe CD I lent you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would get in the way of my studies\Nso I didn't listen to it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your entrance exams are over now,\Nso listen to it. I want to create sounds just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that interested \Nin rock music and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's different! ZHIEND is not \Nrock music! It's post-rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You boasted that before, too.\NLike, I don't understand what you mean at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I wasn't able to enter that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have something important to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I'd have both of you enter a boarding school\Nto further develop your talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just about to sign with \Na record label, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you put that off for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I can live on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be grateful of that\Nbecause of our family's financial situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually the reverse... we'll be\Nbetter off financially if you both go to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, the reverse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao is good at studying,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm an idiot that only \Nknows how to play a guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's exactly\Nwhat they acknowledged you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is that place a specialized school for music?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with both of us going together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, we saw my mother grovel on the ground\Nand beg for the first time in our lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mother, who raised us\Nfor the longest time by herself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That place looked like a school on the outside,\Nand I immediately made a few friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, every day after classes were over,\NI was forced to take something like a physical exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposedly in the same school,\Nbut I couldn't see my brother at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I tried to look for my brother,\Nmy friends would always stop me from doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, my brother had been turned\Ninto an experimental subject the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's ability was to \Nmake air vibrate to his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He used that ability \Nduring a live performance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to change the sound of his guitar\Ninto all sorts of sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how they found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scientists believed that the ability can be used\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to jam communications, or \Neven jack the airwaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I finally was able to meet \Nmy brother a year later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By then, he was no longer\Nthe big brother I remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't even recognize \Nthat I was his little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The friends that were trying\Nto distance me from my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,were all fake friends \Nprepared by the scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why they were \Nexamining me every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...was because if one sibling has an ability,\Nchances are high that the other sibling will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swore in my heart\Nthat I won't trust anyone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I snuck out of that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have met the one person I can put\Nmy trust in, and that's how I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That person is—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting off at the next stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nao Tomori. I'm here \Nto see my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So her first name is Nao.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's in room 12. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take him outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's within our \Ngrounds, there are no issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The painkillers have worn off again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... what in the \Nworld is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's composing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my big brother thinking \Nhe is playing a guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The grunts you hear is the main melody line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh man, he ruined another futon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go outside?\NThis time of day is when you see the best scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this special an environment...\Nhow in the world did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to the \None person I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He transferred my brother to the hospital\Nin the most beautiful location free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone out there \Nthat will go this far...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He shows no interest after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, perhaps there will be a drug soon\Nthat can cure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is researching how \Nto save patients like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the scientists,\Npeople with abilities are like batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it runs out of power, they can just experiment\Nwith another person who has an ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no merit for them to help\Nprevious holders of abilities that end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know whether or not\Nsomething will happen to us tomorrow, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say scary stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about you choose your words a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really have a hard time, don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sympathizing?\NStop that. You're nothing but a cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed... this is so unlike me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think the student council was \Nsomething that keeps me this busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Yu, you're part \Nof the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first I'm hearing of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please eat Ayu's special \NRolling Vegetable Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto refresh yourself and rid today's fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I have a special ability, there is the possibility\Nthat Ayumi has an ability as well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were to be captured...\NAyumi will end up just like Tomori...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So sweet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um... this curry...\Ncan it be that the secret ingredient...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the secret recipe of the\NOtosaka household - the pizza sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this point, I can't think this tastes\Nany different from the omelet rice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's part of your daily routine\Nor not, but hurry up and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to see a comet today,\Nso I am deeply moved, and go to sleep in excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty skillful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, the comet I really want \Nto see is a different one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a comet with a long orbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a comet that swings by\Nonly once every few centuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have comets like that, huh...
